WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.550
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:05.110
for joining us tonight. We're excited

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.190
you're here, and I'm excited to be here. We

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:10.230
have work to do. I've been going

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:11.990
over some things that I could share

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.470
with you today and what the Lord has

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:16.390
been talking to me about over the

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:19.189
last several days. I've been taking my

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:21.349
time and not doing as many live streams

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:27.509
because

00:00:27.519 --> 00:00:28.870
of what the Holy Spirit has been

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:33.350
instructing me on. So,

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:35.430
let me start off with this:

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.430
He said, I want you to go

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:39.030
back to the basics. I want you to go

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:40.790
back to the foundations of

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:43.830
where you came from. Don't forget where

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:46.470
you came from; the books you've read,

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:48.310
the things that have ministered to you,

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:51.510
read them again. Go over them again.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:53.270
Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:55.350
the word of God. And people that are

00:00:55.360 --> 00:00:57.590
more mature than you, you can learn from

00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:00.069
them. People that have been in ministry

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:01.670
longer than you, you can learn from

00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:03.110
them.

00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:05.590
I don't know everything, of course, and

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:09.270
being a newbie in this,

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:11.590
I learn from people who have walked it

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:14.070
longer than I have as far as ministry

00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:17.270
goes. It always goes back to

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:19.429
this book. I know this isn't that

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:21.830
old,

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:25.910
but I don't even know this man,

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:28.070
John Bevere,

00:01:28.080 --> 00:01:32.469
but The Awe of God has changed our life.

00:01:32.479 --> 00:01:35.990
I'm telling you,

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.310
I look forward to my wife

00:01:38.320 --> 00:01:41.030
reading me this book. She reads it to me

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:43.910
every day. We go over the chapters and

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:46.310
she highlights and marks it all up.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.149
Then she found out that there are YouTube

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:50.950
videos that talk about each chapter that

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:54.630
John Bevere wrote.

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:57.030
So we listen to it, and

00:01:57.040 --> 00:02:00.069
we go over it again, and we talk about it

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:02.789
where we are in ministry. I've

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:04.630
always said the first three chapters,

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:06.709
you know, because I feel like if I

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:09.669
can just get you to read part of it, if

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:12.070
it ministers to Diana and me so much, I

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:14.390
pray that it would minister to you.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:17.750
I don't recommend stuff very easily. I

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:20.390
don't believe in selling books a lot

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:21.750
unless the Holy Spirit has led

00:02:21.760 --> 00:02:24.550
you to,

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:26.869
but this book right here, I'm going

00:02:26.879 --> 00:02:32.710
to tell you, it has changed my life.

00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:35.350
I cannot wait until

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:39.910
he has a new book on March

00:02:39.910 --> 00:02:39.920
3rd.

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:43.430
It's about Jesus's return.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:45.030
Now,

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:47.750
Diana said he made the comment that

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:49.589
everything that he's preached up until

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:51.670
now has changed or something like that.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:54.229
I hope, you know,

00:02:54.239 --> 00:02:56.070
I don't know what that means, so I'm not

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:58.790
going to add to it or take away from it.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:01.750
But I want to say this: this book,

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:03.430
sir, I don't know if you watch our

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:05.190
broadcast, but I'm going to tell you,

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:08.550
you got an A+ from me on this one.

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:12.710
Not that that matters, but it does

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:16.390
to me and my wife. Chapter

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:20.470
12, 13, 14 is probably some of the most

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.790
important chapters. I told Diana, I

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:24.390
said, I read over them and read over

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:26.550
them. There

00:03:26.550 --> 00:03:26.560
are

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:29.030
times whenever I do these live

00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:30.710
streams

00:03:30.720 --> 00:03:32.710
and the presence of the Lord is so thick

00:03:32.720 --> 00:03:37.350
in my house, and there's so much chatter

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:39.910
on the live stream.

00:03:39.920 --> 00:03:41.990
He has a quote right here

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:44.309
that I thought was really beautiful.

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:47.270
Here is the bottom line, the truth:

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:50.390
Where the Lord is reverenced, His

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:53.750
presence

00:03:53.750 --> 00:03:53.760
manifests.

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:56.710
I've thought about that a lot.

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:03.429
If we reverence Him,

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:05.750
He

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:05.760
manifests.

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:09.110
The fear of the Lord

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:12.309
is the beginning of wisdom, but

00:04:12.319 --> 00:04:17.349
the awe of Him, the

00:04:17.349 --> 00:04:17.359
reverence—there's

00:04:17.359 --> 00:04:19.830
so much that I

00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:21.270
could pull out of this, and I could have

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:23.670
Diana read these highlights of all these

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:25.350
underlying things, we'd be here all

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:29.510
night,

00:04:29.520 --> 00:04:31.749
but there's so much of this book that I

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:39.830
don't know how else to describe it

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:44.310
to you.

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:46.310
Like I said, I don't sell or push

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:47.909
books. I don't do that. I have

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:49.110
everybody and their brother trying to

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:50.870
give me their book to push on

00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:54.230
my channel, but I'm going

00:04:54.230 --> 00:04:54.240
to

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:56.710
tell you, he's never talked to me and

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:59.350
I've never talked to him,

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:00.870
but this book

00:05:00.870 --> 00:05:00.880
has

00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:04.710
blessed me. So,

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.670
she read it to me most of the day

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:10.230
going over these chapters just because I

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:13.590
don't want to get off track.

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:15.670
There's so much that the Lord, as I was

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:17.670
ministering,

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:19.510
praying over our

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:22.070
house and praying over things.

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:26.710
Last night He visited me

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:29.189
for 45 minutes. He spoke to me about the

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:33.830
future.

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:36.310
It was the most intimate

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:38.150
conversation I've had with Him in a long

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:40.310
time.

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:42.230
This was when He visited here and talked

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:45.110
about President Trump; it was spectacular,

00:05:45.110 --> 00:05:45.120
it

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:47.110
was amazing.

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:51.270
But last night was just a friend

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:53.670
instructing me about the ministry and

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:57.430
about what we're doing.

00:05:57.440 --> 00:06:00.950
I fear Him,

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:03.670
not scared; I reverence Him

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:09.270
with this holy awe, the awe of God.

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:11.430
When I tell you what I'm about to

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:14.309
talk about a little bit tonight, asking

00:06:14.319 --> 00:06:16.950
about why you haven't come

00:06:16.950 --> 00:06:16.960
yet—what

00:06:16.960 --> 00:06:20.710
are you waiting on?

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:22.629
With all the things we see in the earth

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:25.830
right now, what is it that you're

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:27.909
waiting on?

00:06:27.919 --> 00:06:32.550
Why haven't things

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:35.350
escalated like a lot of you

00:06:35.350 --> 00:06:35.360
have

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:36.550
always done? Brandon, He should come

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:37.830
back tomorrow, He should come back

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:40.230
today. Oh, Jesus is coming. I

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:42.710
believe that with all my heart. But what

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:47.029
are we waiting on?

00:06:47.039 --> 00:06:52.710
He gave me scripture.

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:56.309
He gave me

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:02.469
James 5:7.

00:07:02.479 --> 00:07:05.110
Be patient, therefore, brethren, until

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:08.070
the coming of the Lord.

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:12.469
Behold, the husbandman waiteth

00:07:12.479 --> 00:07:17.670
for the precious fruit of the earth,

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:21.270
and hath long patience

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:23.110
for it,

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:25.749
until he receives the early and the

00:07:25.759 --> 00:07:27.830
latter rain.

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:32.309
That's in the New Testament.

00:07:54.479 --> 00:08:00.230
He said to me, I told you,

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:01.990
you're—this

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:03.909
is amazing.

00:08:03.919 --> 00:08:08.629
You're not waiting on me, I'm waiting on

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:10.869
you.

00:08:10.879 --> 00:08:14.469
Bring in my harvest,

00:08:14.479 --> 00:08:16.150
for the harvest is plentiful and the

00:08:16.150 --> 00:08:16.160
laborers

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:18.469
are few.

00:08:18.479 --> 00:08:21.270
I'm waiting on my treasure, my

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:24.629
harvest. Brandon, I'm leaving the 99 to

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:27.830
go after the one. How many times? Until

00:08:27.840 --> 00:08:32.550
He showed me that verse,

00:08:32.560 --> 00:08:34.870
the Lord of the harvest. He came to me

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:36.389
and had holes in His hands. He said, I

00:08:36.399 --> 00:08:37.829
died for all of you. Help me bring them

00:08:37.839 --> 00:08:39.829
in.

00:08:39.839 --> 00:08:43.029
I've given you the farming equipment.

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:45.430
The vast fields of harvest are plentiful,

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:48.230
Brandon.

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:51.190
Do you see the harvest? Help me bring in

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:53.750
the harvest.

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:55.430
I died for every one of them.

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:57.110
He held out His hands. He had

00:08:57.120 --> 00:09:00.710
humongous holes. They went right here.

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:03.269
It

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:05.350
wasn't in the middle. It was right here.

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:08.630
A massive hole.

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:10.230
It went clear into His palm right

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:14.150
here. It was a massive hole. It wasn't

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:16.310
in the center of His hand. It was right

00:09:16.320 --> 00:09:19.990
in here. I want to tell you that

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:22.790
hole is massive.

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:24.389
It took up the whole

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:25.509
bottom half of His hand. You can see

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:27.110
right through it to see

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:29.670
the wheat bowing down

00:09:29.680 --> 00:09:33.910
before Him as He walked by it.

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:36.949
One last call. He said, The sun is

00:09:36.959 --> 00:09:39.269
setting on this dispensation of grace.

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:41.190
If anybody remembers that visitation

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:45.670
that I had and I saw the sun setting

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:48.389
and it was lowered down,

00:09:48.399 --> 00:09:50.310
and He stood there with His priestly

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:53.110
robe, and He kept His voice turned into a

00:09:53.110 --> 00:09:53.120
shofar

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:56.630
and He started saying, One last

00:09:56.640 --> 00:09:59.990
call.

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:01.750
He started screaming and it echoed

00:10:01.760 --> 00:10:05.110
through the valley, One last call.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:08.150
He was calling for the sheep,

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:10.070
and there were all these sheep, all

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:11.670
different kinds, and I told you all about

00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:14.870
it. Then I saw the Father standing, and I

00:10:14.880 --> 00:10:17.910
saw Jesus at

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:21.190
the hoopa, and it was olive leaf, and it

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.870
was cut out, and it was the most

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:24.550
beautiful thing. He was

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:27.829
waiting on the bride,

00:10:27.839 --> 00:10:30.550
and I asked the Lord then, again, He said,

00:10:30.560 --> 00:10:32.069
You're not waiting on me, I'm waiting on

00:10:32.079 --> 00:10:33.590
you. Bring in my harvest, and I'll come

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:37.110
and get you.

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:39.990
There's no urgency in the church for the

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:41.910
second coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:10:41.920 --> 00:10:43.990
There's not enough

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:45.750
anticipation.

00:10:45.760 --> 00:10:48.550
A lot of people, we've become so dull

00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:50.550
and desensitized to the hearing of

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:54.710
it that it's become just

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:56.550
something we throw around. Jesus is

00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:58.230
coming.

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:02.550
But the urgency of the hour

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:06.150
and the expectation of it, we've become

00:11:06.160 --> 00:11:08.710
weary and wallowing, a lot of you. Oh, I

00:11:08.710 --> 00:11:08.720
have

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:11.590
heard that. Brandon, you say

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:13.750
that all the time,

00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:18.230
but I say it because it is real to me.

00:11:18.240 --> 00:11:20.470
And I yell it as loud as I can like John

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:22.550
the Baptist, one crying in the

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:24.949
wilderness, telling you,

00:11:24.959 --> 00:11:27.590
Jesus is coming. He

00:11:27.590 --> 00:11:27.600
is

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:31.990
here,

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:34.230
as the prophets of old cried out

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:37.110
and warned that there was a king coming.

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:39.829
Isaiah, all of them.

00:11:39.839 --> 00:11:44.389
How many times have we heard it?

00:11:44.399 --> 00:11:50.630
I want to be so

00:11:55.600 --> 00:11:57.430
sober

00:11:57.440 --> 00:12:00.870
to bring sobriety to you,

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:03.269
to shake you, to waken you, to tell you

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:12.629
again that our King is coming. It

00:12:12.629 --> 00:12:12.639
is

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:14.550
not something that

00:12:14.560 --> 00:12:16.870
your grandma told you. I am being for

00:12:16.880 --> 00:12:18.550
real.

00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:21.990
Jesus is coming,

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:25.990
but He is waiting for the fruit.

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:28.790
James 5:7.

00:12:28.800 --> 00:12:30.470
If you need to hear it again, I

00:12:30.470 --> 00:12:30.480
will

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:32.870
read it to you again. That is what He

00:12:32.870 --> 00:12:32.880
is

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:37.190
waiting on. The fruit.

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:39.509
The harvest is plentiful and the

00:12:39.519 --> 00:12:42.550
laborers are few. Bring in my harvest.

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:46.550
This is where He was at

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:50.629
as He talked to me last night. There

00:12:50.629 --> 00:12:50.639
are

00:12:50.639 --> 00:12:52.470
a lot of things He said I

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:54.710
cannot talk about

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:57.910
on your platform. It was just

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:00.310
friend talk. He is my friend and I

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:03.190
respect what He asked me to say.

00:13:03.200 --> 00:13:06.550
Therefore, do you have it? Be patient,

00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:09.829
brethren, until the coming of the Lord.

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:14.550
See how the farmer waits for the

00:13:14.560 --> 00:13:17.910
precious fruit of the earth. It

00:13:17.910 --> 00:13:17.920
is

00:13:17.920 --> 00:13:20.230
the New King James

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:20.790
Version.

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:27.430
In the King James

00:13:27.440 --> 00:13:29.269
Version,

00:13:29.279 --> 00:13:31.269
be patient, therefore, brethren, until

00:13:31.279 --> 00:13:33.910
the coming of the Lord. Behold, the

00:13:33.910 --> 00:13:33.920
husbandman

00:13:33.920 --> 00:13:36.629
waiteth

00:13:36.639 --> 00:13:39.509
for the precious fruit of the

00:13:39.519 --> 00:13:43.030
earth and hath long patience. That means He

00:13:43.030 --> 00:13:43.040
is

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:45.030
not in a hurry.

00:13:45.040 --> 00:13:47.430
He

00:13:47.440 --> 00:13:51.430
has long patience for it until He

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:55.590
receives the early and the latter rain.

00:13:55.600 --> 00:13:58.389
He wants a major harvest. Can these

00:13:58.399 --> 00:14:02.870
bones live? That

00:14:02.870 --> 00:14:02.880
is

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:04.150
what He was talking to me

00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:09.269
about, the harvest again.

00:14:09.279 --> 00:14:11.670
He said, There are so many

00:14:11.680 --> 00:14:13.829
that I cannot trust with the finances to

00:14:13.839 --> 00:14:16.150
get it done.

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:19.030
He said, They will receive the money and

00:14:19.040 --> 00:14:20.870
